PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 52 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding which occurred in the Peace River area of BRITISH COLUMBIA in June 2001, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance.
